I just sent an email to my list and I wanted to share it here.
Look around your house.
Is artwork hanging on your walls?
These years of dance or sports or family need to be remembered for a lifetime. Cherished.
The best way is to come into your home seeing an artistic image on your wall that you'll love forever, that will take you back to that time. To that day when the image was made, when your child told you this was the best day ever -- and you didn't even have the print yet.
Look at your walls. It's your home. Your kids won't be there forever.
You cannot put this off any longer.
I have availability for artistic studio shoots in March and April, and I'm even offering some crazy discounts.
If you want rain or color powder, you can register and schedule your summer sessions now.
If you want to do a summer outdoor session, don't wait until the summer to schedule it. Do it now. Commit to it now. How many times have you meant to do it every summer?
Look at your walls. Let's do something crazy, something fun, something completely creative, and let's remember it forever by hanging it on your walls.
There will be days you'll need to see that picture. It will take you back in time. You'll feel the joy, you'll remember the love.
Call us now. 224-288-3076. 
You've already waited. And nothing has happened. Make it happen now. We're scheduling spring and summer sessions now.
